    <item>
      <title>教宗在圣彼得广场主持复活节周日弥撒</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-03-31/pope-overcomes-health-concerns-presides-over-blustery-easter-sunday-mass-in-st-peter-s-square</link>
      <description><![CDATA[罗马（美联社）——教皇方济各克服了对自己健康状况的担忧，主持了复活节周日弥撒，带领约 30,000 人在鲜花盛开的圣彼得广场举行了一年中最重要的礼拜仪式之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-03-31/pope-overcomes-health-concerns-presides-over-blustery-easter-sunday-mass-in-st-peter-s-square</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 31 Mar 2024 08:40:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马萨诸塞州前美国议员威廉·德拉亨特去世，享年 82 岁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-03-31/former-us-rep-william-delahunt-of-massachusetts-has-died-at-age-82</link>
      <description><![CDATA[马萨诸塞州长期担任美国众议员的威廉·D·德拉亨特 (William D. Delahunt) 是民主党的坚定支持者，他推迟了自己从华盛顿退休的时间，以帮助通过前总统巴拉克·奥巴马 (Barack Obama) 的立法议程，他的家人宣布，他因长期患病去世。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-03-31/former-us-rep-william-delahunt-of-massachusetts-has-died-at-age-82</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 31 Mar 2024 08:31:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于未能达成协议，英国与加拿大的贸易壁垒增加</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-31/uk-canada-trade-barriers-to-increase-amid-failure-to-reach-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在两国未能就延期达成协议后，允许英国向加拿大免税销售含有欧盟零部件的产品的规定将于周一到期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-31/uk-canada-trade-barriers-to-increase-amid-failure-to-reach-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 31 Mar 2024 06:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>菲律宾在与中国的争端中改造海事安全办公室</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-31/philippines-revamps-maritime-security-offices-amid-china-spat</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着与北京的南海紧张局势升级，菲律宾总统小费迪南德·马科斯重组了中央海上安全政策机构的职责。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-31/philippines-revamps-maritime-security-offices-amid-china-spat</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 31 Mar 2024 04:23:34 GMT</pubDate>
