    <item>
      <title>埃尔多安在土耳其城市地方选举中面临激烈竞争</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-31/erdogan-faces-tight-race-in-turkish-cities-in-local-elections</link>
      <description><![CDATA[土耳其总统雷杰普·塔伊普·埃尔多安 (Recep Tayyip Erdogan) 及其执政党在周日的地方选举中陷入了激烈的竞争，这是在赢得新任期 10 个月后对领导人权力的关键考验。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-31/erdogan-faces-tight-race-in-turkish-cities-in-local-elections</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 31 Mar 2024 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>苏纳克和斯塔默发布复活节信息，关注即将到来的选举</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-03-30/sunak-and-starmer-issue-easter-messages-with-eye-on-election-to-come</link>
      <description><![CDATA[里希·苏纳克(Rishi Sunak)表示，复活节是一个“暂停和反思”的时刻，而工党领袖凯尔·斯塔默爵士(Sir Keir Starmer)则表示，这是一个“乐观和新开始”的时刻。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-03-30/sunak-and-starmer-issue-easter-messages-with-eye-on-election-to-come</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 30 Mar 2024 22:31:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
